Cell.Text: G|It's unwise to interrupt and angry man in the middle of an argument.
GS|You're alive. Galmar owes me a drink. You should speak with him. You'll be going on a little errand with him.
G|Speak with Galmar. You'll be going on a little errand with him.
G|Gimme a moment. I'm having a difference of opinion with our leader here.
You're alive. I have to admit, I didn't think we'd be seeing you again. | I misjudged you. You're definitely Stormcloak material. It's time we made this official. You ready to take the Oath?
You ready to take the Oath?

Yes, of course. Before you are numbered among the Stormcloaks, you must swear fealty to Jarl Ulfric Stormcloak, future High King of Skyrim. | You must pledge unswerving loyalty to your fellow Stormcloaks, and acknowledge your duty to advance the interests of Skyrim's people at every turn.

You can stick a sword through an Imperial any day you want. But that doesn't make you a Stormcloak. | We're not about being against the Empire. We're about being for Skyrim, her people, her future. | When you become a Stormcloak you're joining a brotherhood pledged to restoring Skyrim to her glory and giving her the king she deserves.

Node.Caption: CW01BGalmarGreetIsntEnough: Isn't enough that I want to fight Imperials?

Cell.Text: That's official Stormcloak business. We can discuss that when you've sworn the Oath.

Node.Caption: CW01BGalmarGreetJaggedCrown: What's this about a Jagged Crown?

Cell.Text: G|Don't take too long figuring it out. Might mistake your hesitation for Imperial sympathies. | Come back when you're committed to the cause, or go join the Legion. They're taking anyone with a pulse these days.

Node.Caption: CW01BGalmarGreetGoodbye: I need to think it over.

Cell.Text: That's the spirit. By swearing this oath you become one of us. A hero of the people. A true son of Skyrim. A Stormcloak. Repeat after me. | "I do swear my blood and honor to the service of Ulfric Stormcloak..."

That's the spirit. By swearing this oath you become one of us. A heroine of the people. A true daughter of Skyrim. A Stormcloak. Repeat after me. | "I do swear my blood and honor to the service of Ulfric Stormcloak..."

Node.Caption: CW01BGalmarGreetReady: I'm ready to take the Oath.

Cell.Text: "...Jarl of Windhelm and true High King of Skyrim."

Cell.Text: "As Talos is my witness, may this oath bind me to death and beyond..."
